Body (HTML):
From skirt to dress to halter to to tube style, pareos are extremely versatile. Wear it however you want, tie it as tight as you want- pareos are a perfect comfy cover up. Title: Sydney Dress
Body (HTML):
A timeless wardrobe staple and a true style essential: the LBD.

Every busy modern woman’s best friend, a little black dress can of course come in many fabrics, cuts and styles… But in terms of curve-flattering fashion, the Sydney Dress [from Vivere] is a tough model to beat. Offering waist-whittling ruching and a figure-skimming ponte knit, this beautiful and clever design compliments an incredible range of curvaceous silhouettes. We love an open neckline and the Sydney Dress delivers, letting you show off some skin yet maintain a little coquettish mystery. We guarantee this versatile dress will get a workout in your wardrobe and see you through many seasons, dinner dates, parties, impromptu outings... 

Hidden back zip closure. Approx. length from shoulder to hem: 42".

Fabrication
Polyester/Rayon/Nylon. Made in the USA.

Care
Dry Clean Only.

Model

And you can wear it as a scoop or a V-neck to fit any look. Perfect for everyday slimming. Layer under any top or blazer. Wear alone tucked into denim, pants, or a skirt. Outlas technology regulates body temperature. Reversible: wear as a scoop or V-neck. Fits up to a G cup comfortably.

71% OLF and tencel, 23% spandex, 6% nylon.

Care:
Machine washable.

Balancing nerdy and cool, this scuba inspired suit has zippers featured on both the top piece and the bottom piece along with a safari print and coverstitch detailing. Title: Rosie Dot Dress
Body (HTML):
This fun take on an LBD has a scoop neck with black on black polka dotted fabric that meets with the sweetheart neckline of the solid fabric to show some skin- but just the right amount. Layered over tights or leggings, under a great coat, or just worn with a great pair of shoes, this slim fit dress is as versatile as a little black dress can be thanks to its comfortable elastic waistband and stretch cotton fabric.

Made in Canada

Belt not included.

Fabrication
85% Cotton, 10% Polyester, 5% Spandex

Care
All Stefanie Bezaire garments are made with the finest care and hopefully once you receive your item you will continue to give it as much love as we have. As a general rule, all items should be washed on delicate with liquid soap and hung or laid flat to dry. Our clothing is not pre-shrunk and where cotton, soy and/or bamboo is included you want to take extra care not to put in the dryer. It may take a bit longer to clean, but trust us; it will be worth it and last much longer. All items are also dry-cleanable if you are so inclined.

Title: Robyn Lawley Ultra Indie Scoop One Piece
Body (HTML):
The indie look is all about no fuss-ease mixed with interesting and beautiful. The simple silhouette in this Robyn Lawley swimsuit makes this suit the perfect grab and go piece, but also highlights the waist. The Multifit soft cup and shelf bra let this suit be as simply easy as can be, but still comfortable. Likewise, the soft fold front leg edges let the suit fit snugly without digging in which creates comfort without sacrificing support. The placement of the beautiful dragonfruit print creates a slimming shape but also features the eye-catching, on-trend mirror effect. The powermesh lining gives tummy control, topping this off as the ultimate any day, anytime suit. This fits women sizes 8, 10, 12, 14, 16 and 18. Designed in Australia.  Made in China.

Title: Fur Trim Anorak
Body (HTML):
There is something to be said for beautiful and classic outerwear. TheFur Trim Anorak puts its own spin on a classic, enough to catch eyes but not enough to ever go out of style.The fur trim jacket has a hooded design, a fold-over collar with press-stud closure, military-inspired tabs on the shoulders and large gold-toned button-up fastenings. The stretch cotton coat features twin contrast cargo pockets on the front, a draw-cord on the rear of the hemline and is designed with an original 17 Sundays brocade print. The coat can function as its own outfit or can complement any ensemble. Being a classic black jacket lets it be worn often, but the distinct print will bring a bit of life into your coat closet and scare away any winter doldrums.

Anorak is 35" long.

Fabrication:
Cotton/Elastane.

Care:
Machine Wash Inside out with like colors, hang to dry.

Model:
Margaret is wearing the Fur Trim Anorak in size 14 (US 12).
